Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:03.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 鬧吧鬧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:06.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣才有樂子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:16.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:16.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:21.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:23.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:25.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,餓死我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:31.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:33.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:35.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:36.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:37.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:38.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:53.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:54.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:56.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:07.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了這樣我們會很難做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:09.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請別客氣 收下我們的一片心意吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:10.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,將這些送給那位...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:13.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你們沒辦法 暫且收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:16.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但大白天的被人看到挺麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:17.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請你們今天先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:22.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:26.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐 我們該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:29.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去肯定會被人告密的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:32.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便不會 也會被異教徒狩獵隊盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:34.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,遲早的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:35.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:37.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那樣 我們會落個什麼下場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:39.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我說妮娜 你冷靜點...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:41.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:45.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便不被盯上 如果約阿希姆的屍體被人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:46.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:49.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:51.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拋棄她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:52.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們...拋棄她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:57.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你又...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:58.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果繼續跟她扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:02.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們真的會完蛋的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:05.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的 艾倫一個人也能活得下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因她真的是那啥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:08.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使將她交給我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們也肯定會善待她的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是已經足夠照顧她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:16.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要我中途拋棄他人 恕難從命!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:18.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你還是艾倫我都不會不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:20.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:23.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好 露加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:24.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:24.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是佩佩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,佩佩被邪教徒狩獵隊...
Comment: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.64,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/--------START---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 有人告發了你!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:05.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要辯解就等到審問之時吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她是露加那邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來最近她們很吃得開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:12.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要被他們強姦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:16.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 你們這些庶民都一個鳥樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:18.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還不給我閉嘴! 吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:22.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些賤民 平時從不祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:27.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦大禍臨頭便輕易地將神之名褂在嘴邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:30.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,膚淺 卑鄙 不知廉恥!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:36.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,居高臨下地鞭打、訓斥他人算什麼本事!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:37.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:39.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,饒了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:47.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,包庇她連你一起抓!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,當人民試圖說出真相的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是如此威脅人民閉嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,亮出手中的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從塔上給人判罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:59.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們莫不是真以為自己是天使?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:02.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說的就這些嗎 姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:02.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,佩佩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:03.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰 是誰如此放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:18.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色劍士?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來得正好!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:28.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是神明保佑 這次絶不會讓你跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽那個女人的口吻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏狩獵魔女的似乎便是你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:38.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我在你們抓到的人中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有胸口刻有烙印的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,烙印?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:44.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不難道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:54.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:55.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,砍成兩半!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,給大姐姐趁現在!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 大姐姐剛才說的話太帥氣了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:05.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺我愛上你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊 這猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的別墅小多洛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:11.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是小多洛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:15.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而剛才出手那位是我的主宅 黑鐵之城格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這便是聖地?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:19.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和垃圾堆弄反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉自我介紹晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫巴克 是這兩棟房子的房東
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是真的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 請不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,傷痛消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退! 閃開閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,向總部報告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:46.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘍囉也問不出什麼來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:49.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只有直接去那裏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:54.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才是說「刻有烙印的女人」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她的下落?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 我要謝你...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一模一樣 跟我們艾倫身上那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我 她在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉 現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 露加姐姐被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 如果真的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,邪教徒狩獵隊查到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:38.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕緊走!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拋棄她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是已經足夠照顧她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何會說出這種話來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:05.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫 你也一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 我會照顧你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能將你拋下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人也挺提心吊膽和寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自上次一別 感覺過了幾十年的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你還和那時一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,精神崩潰 封閉內心...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:32.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...的那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是她嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 劍士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫...啊不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:43.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫卡思嘉來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是她什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:50.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不想答也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我大致清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:00.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:03.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別傻站著 進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:08.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:10.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是邪教徒狩獵隊那些人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:18.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那樣為何沒有破壞的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就少了妮娜的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子 難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來迎接您了 巫女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:05.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算分頭找 可這裏地方這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:08.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小多洛你為什麼一直跟著格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:10.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至幫他找人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那你又為何待在我頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:16.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你不知道卡思嘉長什麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:18.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你就知道了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:21.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我通過腦電波知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:22.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:23.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看到你都在發抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:26.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都是膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:32.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人多的地方應該很難看到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是不是有什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:38.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道是因為狩獵魔女還是什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但大家竟然如此害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:42.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 鬱悶死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,逃離與庫夏人的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏又害怕告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:48.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是越來越墮落了呢 這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那小多洛你不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:50.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:53.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,亂世正是男子漢揚名之際!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:55.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不需要本錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只需一柄劍!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:59.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想拜格斯為師?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:00.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說了不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會因為想學習本領就向別人卑躬屈膝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:07.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,悄然尾隨並將他們的絶學偷到手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:09.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是男子漢!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是賊性不改
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 如果能在這件事賣個人情給他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:17.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也就不需要鬼鬼祟祟地尾隨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是互惠互利!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:22.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:25.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,綁繃帶的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被拐騙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回去報信就要跟丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但他們那麼多人又不能硬來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總之...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...先尾隨!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的拿手本事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,屬下有事報告!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,邪教徒的隱蔽處?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:57.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我身邊這位聲稱他被邪教徒綁架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後從那裏逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,根據他說話的樣子和對地形的描述來看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,並不像是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 全軍出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:06.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,何事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:13.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在難民營押送邪教徒的小隊遭到襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:14.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有數人傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,根據撤退回來那些人的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:19.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人只有一名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:19.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:21.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是身披黑披風
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:23.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,手持堪比其身高長度大劍的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:25.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色劍士!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:26.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 千真萬確
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是上天的安排!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:34.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定不能放跑那個傢伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:38.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你帶我們去邪教徒的隱蔽處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:39.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,中大獎了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:57.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子這裏就是邪教徒的賊窩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,各位!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:03.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚將會成為流傳後世的聖夜吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如今那座塔耍弄詭辯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:11.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成了壓迫及統治吾等的溫床
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:14.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但吾等知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:16.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真正應該崇拜的是誰!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真正擁有力量的是誰!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚 在約定之日來臨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:25.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等主人先給各位展示一下證據
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:31.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她是吾等的巫女!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:36.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,黑魔女!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:40.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這位大人正是吾等信仰的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:42.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是奇蹟!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在這個值得慶祝的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:49.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從信徒選出一位不勝榮幸的幸運兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是跟卡思嘉一起的那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:56.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 感覺不妙啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:14:00.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,慶倖吧! 吾等的女兒妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你企圖獨佔巫女的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,通過這份重任便能贖清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:09.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就將她的心臟取出來!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻給魔女大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後魔女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,將會和雄山羊大人交媾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:19.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成為吾等家族真正的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很不妙!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:23.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦怎麼辦怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:27.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在去叫格斯大哥也來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:35.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 巴克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:36.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我拖延時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你以最快速度去叫大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次聽說你有這種實力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,地利在我這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:52.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有對我刮目相看一點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:05.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒什麼必要我都不太想用這招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為對於今後要仗劍揚名的男子漢來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這招實在是太寒酸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:12.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,扔石子的...小偷...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪你叫伊斯多洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:15.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你會這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:18.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們這群迷信的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:21.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別在散發著一股腐味的巢穴中做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我告發你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:24.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 走吧 巴克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:28.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,扔吧! 直到你的鋼鐵左腕折斷!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:31.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請向格斯大哥多些我的好話!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,將他拖下來!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把他也當作犧牲品!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:40.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不抱團什麼都辦不到的暴徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:43.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們才是實現我野心的犧牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:43.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接招!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢東西!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是全身都是要害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,石子多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:52.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,離開村子一年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:56.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,漫無目的地徘徊在庫夏人和山賊出沒的邊境
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:16:00.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,經歷了多少危險的瞬間和不吃不喝的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但這一切都得到了回報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:05.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在一個天大的機會擺在了我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒理由痛失良機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要過這個關口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:12.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就能抓住通往野心的的端倪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:14.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何也要贏!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都在幹什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:18.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫 趁現在...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:23.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:40.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:54.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:59.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 一到四隊跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,其餘在洞口守著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,出逃者全部逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:04.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,進洞!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,制服他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:15.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,邪教徒 抵抗者殺無赦!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救命!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:20.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:21.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這群傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:26.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:42.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾桑副團長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾桑 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:55.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說邪教徒會在他們的宗教儀式上服用各種藥物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:18:01.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,或許裏面就有這種令人喪失心智的藥物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,藥物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:03.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:08.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點 現在他們的力量是常人的數倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:11.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,藥物? 真的如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺回到了那個時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:22.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看我用魔球打爆你的頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:23.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且魔女狩獵隊一個接一個地進來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這下真的不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個神經病!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死...要死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:52.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我砸!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:53.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 姐姐們 跟我逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:55.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫伊斯多洛 以後再跟你們解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:03.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:05.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,走那邊不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,角卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊摘下來!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救...救...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:39.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞大人 這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:43.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,暫且撤退 重整旗鼓是不是好點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:44.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:47.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小屁孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:49.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何這裏會有一個小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...真正的怪物?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:15.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那他們全都是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:20.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那個夜晚 一模一樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是騎士吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別逃 去戰鬥! 懦夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:40.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看來裏面相當棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 剛才是不是有什麼飛過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:51.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這群怪物!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:05.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,交媾...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成為家族一員...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:39.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個淫蟲雄山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,發你媽逼的情啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.09,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,佩佩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.13,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,有...有什麼在...
